1.1 Background This repository contains source code related to the study: Mapping the world&rsquo;s free-flowing rivers. The scripts and modules described here form part of a &ldquo;free-flowing rivers analysis: or &ldquo;FRA&rdquo;
Free-flowing rivers assessment (FRA). A FRA is an assessment to determine the connectivity status of rivers by taking into consideration both natural connectivity as well as fragmentation from infrastructure, such as dams, roads, urban areas, water use.
Connectivity Status Index (CSI).
